<div class="card fade-in">
    <h3>Feature 9: AI Life Expectancy Predictor</h3>
    <p>Uses Linear Regression (Machine Learning) on historical data to predict values for <strong>2026</strong>.</p>

    <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">Select Country to Predict:</label>
        <select class="form-control" name="country_id" 
                hx-get="/api/feature9/predict" 
                hx-target="#result-area-f9" 
                hx-trigger="change">
            <option value="">-- Select Country --</option>
            {{#countries}}
                <option value="{{id}}">{{name}}</option>
            {{/countries}}
        </select>
    </div>

    <div class="htmx-indicator" style="margin-top:10px; color:#555;">
        Running Algorithm... ðŸ¤–
    </div>

    <div id="result-area-f9" style="margin-top: 20px;"></div>
</div>